        <briefdescription>
<para>Inquiry scan interval in 0.625 ms units Range: 0x0012 to 0x1000. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>According to the Bluetooth Core Specification, only even values are used by the controller; if an odd value is provided, the controller may ignore the LSB or round the value. Applications should use even values to be compliant. </para>
